<h2 id="_3_settings">3. 3) Settings</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The <strong>settings</strong> described below are available for this statistic.</p>
</div>
<div class="imageblock">
<div class="content">
<img src="{{plugin_path('PlentyManual')}}/images/basics/statistics/general-statistics/revenue/assets/EN-ENG-Statistik-Retouren02-SI.png" alt="EN ENG Statistik Retouren02 SI">
