<p><em>Image 2: <strong>returns / credit notes / cancellations</strong> statistic; <strong>settings</strong></em></p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Explanations of the options</p>
</div>
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all spread">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 50%;">
<col style="width: 50%;">
